3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper involves the modeling and analysis of a physical system (diffusive molecular communication), which is a core area of systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the transmission of information through molecules, which can be considered a form of multimedia communication.
